OL,3,CHelp! We Need A Builder: Britain's
OL,4,CSkills Shortage
OL,6,FWe are facing a severe shortage of
OL,7,Fskilled tradespeople - it's estimated
OL,8,Fthe UK needs nearly a million new
OL,9,Frecruits in trades and construction
OL,10,Fover the next decade. At the same time
OL,11,Fdemand is soaring, creating a perfect
OL,12,Fstorm which threatens homeowners,
OL,13,Fbusinesses and the national economy.
OL,14,FSo why are we in this situation and
OL,15,Fwhat can be done about it? Michelle
OL,16,FAckerley has been investigating.
