OL,6,FBuilders, plumbers, joiners and
OL,7,Felectricians, they all play a vital
OL,8,Frole in our economy and society - but
OL,9,Fthere's a problem. Last year, one in
OL,10,Ffive Brits had to cancel or postpone
OL,11,Fprojects on their house due to not
OL,12,Fbeing able to find a suitable
OL,13,Ftradesperson and things don't seem to
OL,14,Fbe improving.
