OL,4,CSkills Shortage
OL,6,FA national shortage of skilled
OL,7,Ftradespeople is estimated to cost the
OL,8,FUK #12bn a year and one third of
OL,9,Fskilled trades people are over 50 and
OL,10,Fwill likely retire within the next ten
OL,11,Fyears. Nearly half of UK homeowners
OL,12,Fhave struggled to hire a tradesperson
OL,13,Ffor their projects or repairs, with
OL,14,Fthe top reasons cited being "no
OL,15,Favailability".
