OL,4,CSkills Shortage
OL,6,FAttracting women to trades professions
OL,7,Fis another problem - according to the
OL,8,Flatest ONS data, just 2.1% of people
OL,9,Fworking in skilled construction and
OL,10,Fbuilding trades were women and yet
OL,11,Fmany homeowners would prefer to hire a
OL,12,Ffemale tradesperson to work in their
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,FIn the here and now if you're thinking
OL,16,Fof taking on building work, finding
OL,17,Fthe right trader is vital - and if
OL,18,Fsomeone is available immediately and
OL,19,Fit seems too good to be true, assume
OL,20,Fit probably is.
